  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "Who was the most powerful Uchiha, and why?",
  "response": "The title of the \"most powerful Uchiha\" is subjective and often debated among fans of the *Naruto* series, as different members of the Uchiha clan excelled in different areas. However, there are a few key candidates who are often considered for this title:\n\n### 1. **Madara Uchiha**\n   - **Reasons:**\n     - Madara was one of the founders of the Leaf Village and the first Uchiha to awaken the Eternal Mangeky\u014d Sharingan.\n     - He later became the Ten-Tails Jinch\u016briki, gaining immense power and near-godlike abilities.\n     - He possessed both the Rinnegan and the Sharingan, allowing him to master a wide range of techniques, including the devastating Perfect Susanoo.\n     - His combat experience and strategic genius made him a formidable opponent, capable of taking on entire armies and multiple Kage-level shinobi.\n\n### 2. **Sasuke Uchiha**\n   - **Reasons:**\n     - Sasuke awakened the Eternal Mangeky\u014d Sharingan after receiving Itachi's eyes and later gained the Rinnegan from Hagoromo \u014ctsutsuki.\n     - His mastery of space-time ninjutsu, Amaterasu, and his ability to control the Tailed Beasts made him incredibly powerful.\n     - Sasuke was able to fight on par with Naruto Uzumaki, who was the reincarnation of Asura \u014ctsutsuki, showcasing his immense strength.\n     - His versatility and adaptability in battle made him one of the strongest shinobi in history.\n\n### 3. **Itachi Uchiha**\n   - **Reasons:**\n     - Itachi was a prodigy who awakened his Sharingan at a young age and later mastered the Mangeky\u014d Sharingan.\n     - His genjutsu, particularly Tsukuyomi, was nearly unmatched, and he could defeat opponents without physical combat.\n     - He also possessed the Yata Mirror and Totsuka Blade, which made his Susanoo virtually invincible.\n     - Despite his health issues, Itachi remained one of the most intelligent and skilled Uchiha in history.\n\n### 4. **Obito Uchiha (Tobi)**\n   - **Reasons:**\n     - Obito awakened his Mangeky\u014d Sharingan and gained Kamui, a space-time ninjutsu that made him nearly untouchable.\n     - He later became the Ten-Tails Jinch\u016briki, gaining immense power and the ability to use the Six Paths techniques.\n     - His control over the Akatsuki and his role in orchestrating much of the series' events demonstrated his strategic brilliance.\n\n### Final Verdict:\nWhile Itachi and Sasuke are often praised for their skills and intelligence, **Madara Uchiha** is generally regarded as the most powerful Uchiha due to his overwhelming strength, mastery of multiple dojutsu, and godlike abilities as the Ten-Tails Jinch\u016briki. However, Sasuke's Rinnegan and his role in the Fourth Great Ninja War make him a close contender, especially in the *Boruto* era.",
  "temperature": 1.0,
